<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Discover The World</title>

<style>

body{
margin:0;
font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
background:#f5f7fb;
}

/* Main container */

.container{
display:flex;
justify-content:space-between;
align-items:center;
padding:60px;
}

/* Left side */

.left{
width:45%;
}

.left h1{
font-size:50px;
margin:0;
}

.left h1 span{
color:#2b6cb0;
font-family:cursive;
}

.left p{
color:#555;
margin-top:15px;
}

.buttons{
margin-top:20px;
}

.btn1{
background:#2b6cb0;
color:white;
padding:10px 20px;
border:none;
border-radius:20px;
cursor:pointer;
}

.btn2{
margin-left:15px;
background:white;
border:1px solid #ccc;
padding:10px 20px;
border-radius:20px;
cursor:pointer;
}

/* Right side image */

.right img{
width:350px;
}

/* Stats boxes */

.stats{
display:flex;
gap:20px;
margin-left:60px;
margin-top:20px;
}

.box{
background:#2b6cb0;
color:white;
padding:15px 25px;
border-radius:10px;
text-align:center;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<div class="left">

<h1><span>Discover</span><br>The World</h1>

<p>
Lets embark on a global journey, immersing ourselves in diverse cultures
and creating unforgettable memories as we travel the world.
</p>

<div class="buttons">
<button class="btn1">Explore More</button>
<button class="btn2">Watch Demo</button>
</div>

</div>

<div class="right">
<img src="https://wallpapers.com/images/hd/mountain-travel-inspiration-xt4mt3oewkg9ypao.jpg">
</div>

</div>

<div class="stats">

<div class="box">64+ <br> Countries</div>
<div class="box">24M+ <br> Per Year User</div>
<div class="box">0.3K+ <br> Experiences</div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
